Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.22,0:00:18.15,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算翻过所有的杂志也没有用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.51,0:00:22.11,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能在这摇头叹息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.39,0:00:26.50,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本找不到 与我相称的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.69,0:00:30.54,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世纪末的流行色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.86,0:00:34.58,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都无法 讨得你的欢心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.78,0:00:38.38,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉让你失望了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.54,0:00:43.17,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如履薄冰这样不稳的步伐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.71,0:00:47.34,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摇摇晃晃的又有什么不好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.50,0:00:51.35,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此还是得向前迈进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.74,0:00:56.02,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说  一点也不成问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.97,0:01:05.07,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这根本不像我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.16,0:01:08.87,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你  别用那种冷冷的眼神望着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.06,0:01:12.71,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我照着自己的步调去做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.07,0:01:16.90,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的话我很快就会崩溃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.41,0:01:20.90,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如履薄冰这样不稳的步伐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.44,0:01:24.88,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摇摇晃晃的又有什么不好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.33,0:01:29.41,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此还是得向前迈进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.72,0:01:34.06,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说  一点也不成问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.34,0:22:00.35,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  真正的所在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.84,0:22:06.02,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  这就是爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.26,0:22:11.44,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在冰冷的黑暗中  伸手寻找温暖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.53,0:22:17.32,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天  奇迹也一定会发生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.87,0:22:30.20,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic 如果有爱 就绝对有具体的形式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.71,0:22:41.26,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic 现在 在我手中 有诞生的气息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.47,0:22:49.48,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是精神饱满  也不能  太过勉强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.86,0:22:54.78,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  把些微的勇气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.28,0:23:05.96,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  凝聚起来  培育茁壮吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.56,0:00:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在瞬间明白所有真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.61,0:00:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要开始就不会停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.44,0:00:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,热热闹闹的暑假才刚刚开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.73,0:00:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,园子的对象是什么样的人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.92,0:00:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.58,0:00:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一个外表看似小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.60,0:00:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智慧却过于常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.74,0:00:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字是 名侦探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.38,0:01:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在盛夏到伊豆去做海水浴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.30,0:01:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟小兰却遇到了一件奇怪的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.56,0:01:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为园子竟然交了一个姓道胁的男朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.94,0:01:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 就在她开开心心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.23,0:01:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着请吃晚餐的道胁先生去接她的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.68,0:01:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,园子却遭到了不明人士的攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.80,0:02:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是我多心才觉得总有人在监视我们吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.93,0:02:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兰说的那个在哪见过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.07,0:02:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴眼镜的人也很可疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.55,0:02:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有攻击园子的歹徒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.20,0:02:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人真的是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.40,0:02:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个单纯的小偷吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.60,0:02:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,园子危险的夏日物语(后篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.29,0:02:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.53,0:02:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒的餐厅哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.34,0:02:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这里好像没有什么客人来嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.65,0:02:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们好像来得太早了一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.39,0:02:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的不跟我们过去啊？ 园子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.53,0:03:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我昨天晚上在被窝里面一直想起那个男的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.88,0:03:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就没办法好好睡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.71,0:03:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想在这里睡一会儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.19,0:03:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 那好可惜哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.94,0:03:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在小冰箱里面放了很多的饮料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.19,0:03:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你渴的话自己拿吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.69,0:03:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.95,0:03:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们走啰 园子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.51,0:03:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们尽管慢慢吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.36,0:03:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你觉得睡够了的话呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.16,0:03:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你待会就自己来餐厅哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.38,0:03:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.09,0:03:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的海鲜御膳真的非常好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.26,0:03:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本来是想让园子也尝一尝的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.61,0:03:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太可惜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.29,0:03:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,园子她没有问题吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.17,0:03:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那辆车子还在发动中耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.58,0:03:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把冷气打开了 放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.84,0:04:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好丰盛哦 这是一人份吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.18,0:04:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 既丰盛又便宜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.60,0:04:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是这家餐厅受欢迎的秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.51,0:04:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大清早的就吃全餐啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.44,0:04:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 这里的料理没话说吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.08,0:04:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 好好吃哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.41,0:04:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃得快要撑死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.74,0:04:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要谢谢你请客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.49,0:04:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都觉得有点对不起园子了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.10,0:04:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是旅馆的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.85,0:04:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也常常到这家餐厅来吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.32,0:04:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 今天是我第一次来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.72,0:04:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过那个咖啡色头发的女孩上哪去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.89,0:04:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么一直没有见到她人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.52,0:04:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说园子啊 她昨天晚上没有睡好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.11,0:04:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正在外面的车子里补眠呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.20,0:04:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.10,0:05:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道胁哥哥的车子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.18,0:05:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车子怎么会动呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.26,0:05:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 前面就是悬崖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.32,0:05:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢惠顾 欢迎下次再来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.04,0:05:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.68,0:05:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有付钱啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.88,0:05:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.86,0:05:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开车锁的工具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.20,0:05:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手煞车被人放下来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.11,0:05:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,园子 快醒醒啊 园子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.07,0:05:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样跑根本没有办法使力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.70,0:05:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完了 没剩多少距离了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.69,0:05:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 离开这辆车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.21,0:06:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.22,0:06:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,园子 快抓住我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.30,0:06:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.92,0:06:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.24,0:06:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好 大家都没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.52,0:06:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.68,0:06:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你当时为什么不把手煞车拉上呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.53,0:06:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你少胡说 我当然有拉上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.24,0:06:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我没有拉手煞车的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.73,0:06:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车子早就已经掉到悬崖下面去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.55,0:06:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才有人把手煞车放下来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.89,0:06:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他利用开车锁的工具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.70,0:06:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把车锁给撬开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.31,0:06:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是企图谋害园子姐姐的不明人士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.96,0:07:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.07,0:07:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,园子在车上睡觉的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.08,0:07:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某个人把车锁给撬开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.28,0:07:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后再把手煞车给放下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.12,0:07:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么一来就可以慢慢地让车子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.56,0:07:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺着坡道滑到悬崖下面去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.95,0:07:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据潜水人员的报告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.17,0:07:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那辆掉到海里面的车子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.98,0:07:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手煞车的确没有拉起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.38,0:07:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外我们还在路上发现了这个东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.52,0:07:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是开车锁的工具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.18,0:07:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歹徒是一个行家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.60,0:07:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面的指纹都已经被擦干净了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.98,0:07:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外 还有没有什么线索？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.44,0:07:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.35,0:07:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前唯一发现的是就在停车的那个地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.83,0:07:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流了一滩从车子空调上流出来的水而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.19,0:07:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,园子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.39,0:07:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时你有没有看到可疑的人物在车子的附近徘徊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.79,0:07:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 因为昨天没怎么睡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.21,0:07:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以刚才在车子里面睡得很熟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.65,0:08:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真要说起来 从我们到伊豆以后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.37,0:08:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都会莫名其妙出现在我们附近的可疑人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.92,0:08:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边倒是有一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.02,0:08:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 请问你是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.72,0:08:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是在他们下榻旅馆服务的职员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.81,0:08:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天会到这里来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.33,0:08:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为旅馆白天的工作没有那么繁重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.34,0:08:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才抽了点空到这里来喝杯茶的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.00,0:08:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个家伙绝对不是凶手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.10,0:08:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车子向下滑的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.88,0:08:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就已经走到我们当时吃饭的餐厅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.88,0:08:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果说他是先将车门撬开之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.72,0:08:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将手煞车放下再赶到餐厅的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.79,0:08:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他从餐厅入口进去的时候 我们应该会注意到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.16,0:08:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据餐厅的人表示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.61,0:08:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餐厅的后门当时是上着锁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.31,0:08:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们注意到他的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.40,0:08:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他正好从洗手间出来的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.83,0:09:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餐厅的洗手间里没有可以爬到外面的窗户
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.41,0:09:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然也不可能是道胁先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.11,0:09:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他一直跟我们在同一张桌子上进餐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.73,0:09:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中间也没有离席过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.24,0:09:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.82,0:09:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最可疑的就是那个一直跟踪监视我们的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.79,0:09:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他到底是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.40,0:09:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么在场的各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.59,0:09:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,详细经过等到了局里再说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.25,0:09:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 大家请上车吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.64,0:09:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要坐车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.12,0:09:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我现在真的很不想再坐车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.18,0:09:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有点害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.06,0:09:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样园子你就跟我一块走到警局好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.62,0:09:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这里走过去不是很远
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.53,0:09:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一边看看风景还可以缓解情绪怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.05,0:09:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 就这么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.40,0:09:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请…请等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.60,0:09:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你又遭到攻击那可怎么办才好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.33,0:10:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,园子你的头发又是咖啡色的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.50,0:10:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个歹徒跟那个命案的凶手很有可能是同一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.13,0:10:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官你不用太担心啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.36,0:10:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想他再怎么大胆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.69,0:10:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不可能光天化日下手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.13,0:10:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 要是有个万一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.82,0:10:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你放心吧 警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.82,0:10:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有道胁先生陪着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.48,0:10:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真要有什么万一的话还有小兰保护啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.31,0:10:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 这样你们可别绕到其它地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.62,0:10:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要直接到警局
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.05,0:10:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.37,0:10:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是昨天在旅馆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.94,0:10:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是今天在车上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.51,0:10:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真是多灾多难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.97,0:10:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,园子 你真的没有什么印象吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.28,0:10:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.69,0:10:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从此可见 你有独特的魅力哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.26,0:10:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歹徒为什么要攻击园子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.33,0:10:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.28,0:10:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果要她的命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.92,0:11:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不在他撬开车门的时候一刀刺死她呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.25,0:11:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何必要故意让车子滑动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.26,0:11:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺势掉下悬崖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.17,0:11:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种方式花的功夫反而更多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.01,0:11:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 我们本来打算吃完饭后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.45,0:11:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就顺便回家而把行李都放车上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.38,0:11:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在全都一起烧光了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.53,0:11:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 怎么偏偏是我碰上这种倒霉的事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.42,0:11:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们还不算什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.16,0:11:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我损失的可是车子耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.49,0:11:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说得对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.24,0:11:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从认识了我以后 实在给你添太多麻烦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.45,0:11:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实也没那么严重啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.61,0:11:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你拍的照片比起来这不算什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.67,0:11:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照片可是金钱买不到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.23,0:11:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果到最后留下来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.78,0:11:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有那一张照片了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.46,0:11:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一张？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.65,0:11:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.35,0:11:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是要给新一看的那张照片啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.79,0:11:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直带在身上 你可以放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.21,0:11:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还带着啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.15,0:11:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你再闹的话我可要生气啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.23,0:11:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 就是照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.16,0:12:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歹徒真正的目的的果然是要销毁那些照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.43,0:12:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以他才有必要将车子跟园子的行李一起摔下悬崖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.65,0:12:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.49,0:12:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歹徒怎么会认为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.77,0:12:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,园子拍到了他不能为人所知的照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.71,0:12:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也看过园子拍的那些照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.87,0:12:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面根本没有类似的照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.16,0:12:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说有我疏忽掉的地方吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.16,0:12:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是那个家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.17,0:12:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们好像被人家跟踪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.33,0:12:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是凶手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.10,0:12:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要用跑的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.31,0:12:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就跑吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.67,0:12:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们赶快追上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.13,0:13:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑到这种树林里来反而会更危险的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.97,0:13:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会 这样才安全啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.27,0:13:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.20,0:13:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 我们兵分两路把他包围起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.39,0:13:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.63,0:13:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他就是凶手的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.42,0:13:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么还想对园子不利呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.66,0:13:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照片早就烧掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.84,0:13:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.23,0:13:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.70,0:13:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是昨天发现尸体的树林
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.03,0:13:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们前天晚上经过这的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.86,0:13:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电车也刚好经过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.00,0:13:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么 有什么不对劲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.86,0:14:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 把他们给跟丢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.82,0:14:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下事情可就麻烦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.76,0:14:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底闹够了没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.86,0:14:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是以为我们会一直逃避
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.73,0:14:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就大错特错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.79,0:14:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.51,0:14:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁叫你要穿着一双拖鞋就跑到树林里面来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.47,0:14:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拖鞋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.25,0:14:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.95,0:14:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天在旅馆里面攻击园子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.92,0:14:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才又让车子坠落悬崖对不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.52,0:14:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.79,0:14:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你再怎么解释都没有用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.08,0:14:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你手上的毛就是证据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.98,0:14:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要好好的看清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.44,0:14:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,园子昨天晚上在你的手臂上留下的齿痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.95,0:14:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.04,0:14:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会没有齿痕呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.43,0:14:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在另外一只手对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.79,0:14:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只手上也没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.27,0:14:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会呢 你到底是谁啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.14,0:14:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你问我是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.28,0:15:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是千叶县警局的刑警
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.87,0:15:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要以为亮出了这种证件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.52,0:15:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的人就会轻而易举的相信你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.44,0:15:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可告诉你 我父亲以前也做过警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.04,0:15:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我清楚得很
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.57,0:15:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有必要要出示警察身份的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.71,0:15:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一定要翻出永久用纸的第一页
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.75,0:15:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是正确的做法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.40,0:15:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫寺林省二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.54,0:15:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.47,0:15:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我正在追踪一个案件的嫌疑犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.78,0:15:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫌疑犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.10,0:15:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兰姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.29,0:15:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般穿拖鞋的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.28,0:15:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是不穿袜子的对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.80,0:15:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 是没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.79,0:15:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.84,0:15:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,园子有危险了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.85,0:15:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.06,0:15:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我踩到树枝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.93,0:15:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子我们跑进树林里来真的是错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.44,0:15:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要紧吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.01,0:15:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,齿痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.65,0:16:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么会吓成这个样子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.28,0:16:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本没什么好怕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.58,0:16:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是昨晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.13,0:16:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在我腿上留下的齿痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.29,0:16:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.13,0:16:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实园子昨晚咬到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.11,0:16:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是手臂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.27,0:16:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是小腿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.42,0:16:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光线太暗她才误会了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.59,0:16:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凶手会认为园子拍到照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.01,0:16:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想可能是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.74,0:16:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电车行驶时电架摩擦所发出的光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.31,0:16:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在犯案的时候光线来自身后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.91,0:16:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行凶之后又看到园子拿着照相机从树林的旁边经过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.66,0:16:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他才会误会的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.98,0:16:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他以为园子看到他跟被害者在一起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.50,0:16:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 那个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.09,0:16:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也说过那句话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.73,0:16:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别放在心上 你不管怎么穿都很迷人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.28,0:16:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 浴衣和泳装也一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.85,0:17:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,园子到这之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.59,0:17:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有在前天看烟火的时候才穿过浴衣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.37,0:17:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们昨天才跟这个家伙认识
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.13,0:17:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不可能看过园子穿浴衣的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.93,0:17:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.54,0:17:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我没有早注意到这一点呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.33,0:17:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.87,0:17:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点把照片拿出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.84,0:17:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你拍了那张要给那个侦探看的照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.66,0:17:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你看来也许以为那是情侣亲热的画面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.92,0:17:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你拍到我行凶的过程了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.91,0:17:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就和这一幕一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.63,0:17:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四…四个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.51,0:17:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说道胁先生杀了四个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.02,0:17:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果昨天的被害人也是他杀的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.39,0:17:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该就是四个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.77,0:17:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不知道他为何只找咖啡色头发的女子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.72,0:17:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从很久以前我就已经盯上他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.95,0:17:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候只是为了一件偷车案逮捕他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.16,0:17:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于杀人案件证据还不足够
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.20,0:17:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是听说伊豆这里也发生了类似的案件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.37,0:17:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才过来看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.36,0:17:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然又让我看到那个家伙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.76,0:18:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我赶到的时候他已经犯案了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.15,0:18:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想不通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.14,0:18:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时他明明一直呆在餐厅里头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.97,0:18:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能让车子自己滑动呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.55,0:18:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用冰块啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.66,0:18:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.59,0:18:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他车上有小冰箱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.16,0:18:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他先拿出一个楔子形状的冰块
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.14,0:18:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放在左轮的轮胎下面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.14,0:18:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻止车子向前滑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.19,0:18:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后假装对着留在车内的园子说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.03,0:18:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺势把手煞车放了下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.61,0:18:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着再把开车锁的工具丢在路上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.68,0:18:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为的就是要混淆警方的搜查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.14,0:18:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.88,0:18:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他之所以会预留两个停车格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.55,0:18:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是为了避免其它车子会停在他车子的前面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.18,0:18:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都会以为那只是车上空调流出的水而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.52,0:18:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.05,0:18:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么他只攻击咖啡色头发的女子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.74,0:18:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.24,0:18:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被女朋友狠心的甩掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.40,0:18:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.30,0:18:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.79,0:19:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只要一看到你这种聒噪的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.45,0:19:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心里就会自然而然的开始冒火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.82,0:19:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你和那个陷我于万丈深渊的女人一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.55,0:19:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都有一头咖啡色的头发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.58,0:19:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们快看那里 那不是园子吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.37,0:19:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.85,0:19:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.97,0:19:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 这是为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.49,0:19:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么对我有意的男人都是这种人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.30,0:19:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老天爷我恨你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.36,0:19:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要紧吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.96,0:19:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.69,0:19:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你的手...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.82,0:19:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说这个啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.19,0:19:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.97,0:19:53.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直觉得在哪里见过那个戴眼镜的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.55,0:19:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是在比赛的会场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.48,0:19:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是杯户高中空手道的主将
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.06,0:20:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人称「踢击美男子」的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.64,0:20:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京极真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.96,0:20:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.38,0:20:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个家伙还真是危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.70,0:20:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不是有我这种悠闲人常在旁边出现那就完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.18,0:20:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠闲人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.41,0:20:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说你一直都在我的身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.18,0:20:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直跟在你们的后面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.52,0:20:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到你们进树林之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.68,0:20:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经有被当成跟踪狂的心理准备了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.90,0:20:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个家伙在遇到你们之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.73,0:20:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也曾经跟两三个女孩子搭讪过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.49,0:20:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我一直有点担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.59,0:20:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要保护我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.40,0:20:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们两个又不认识
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.45,0:20:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也许不知道我是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.43,0:20:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我曾经在空手道的比赛会场看过你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.78,0:20:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时拼了命地在为朋友加油的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.40,0:20:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的倩影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.58,0:20:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是没有想到你会这么巧投宿到我家的旅馆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.62,0:21:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.31,0:21:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种故意要挑起男人注意那种类似内衣的穿着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.02,0:21:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我劝你以后能不穿还是不要再穿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.41,0:21:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.64,0:21:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是对你有好感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.46,0:21:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万众之中的一个男孩的心意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.92,0:21:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你不领情也无所谓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.36,0:23:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京极要到外国留学了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.47,0:23:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.91,0:23:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个在那之后不是相处得很好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.91,0:23:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他说日本已经没有强劲的对手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.92,0:23:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他要到那里去深造
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.01,0:23:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.17,0:23:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一起去看棒球社的友谊赛吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.04,0:23:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方是高一的棒球主力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.39,0:23:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说不但人长得帅 也很受欢迎呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.15,0:23:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是还说要等京极回来的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.67,0:23:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.99,0:23:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.49,0:23:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.72,0:23:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钥匙在水里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.46,0:23:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,窗户
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.13,0:23:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.32,0:24:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般人是不可能从那个地方进出的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.84,0:24:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他到底是用了什么手法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.09,0:24:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让这个浴室变成密室的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.89,0:24:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.41,0:24:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水中的钥匙密室事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.05,0:24:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.48,0:24:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜡笔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.26,0:24:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回的事件是钥匙上的铁圈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.74,0:24:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说啥 我听不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.10,0:24:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘻嘻 不告诉你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.20,0:24:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这梗还真老
